<!DOCTYPE>

<html>
    <head>
        <title>File Metadata Microservice</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    </head>

    <body>
        <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center">File Metadata Microservice</h1>

        <h3>User stories:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li> I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload.</li>
            <li>When I submit something, I will receive the file meta data within the JSON response</li>
        </ul>

        <form class="form-inline" action="/getMeta" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <div class="form-group">
            <input type="file" class="form-control" name="file" required>
        </div>
        
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Get Info</button>
        </form>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
